headline: Accenture Invests in Lyzr to Bring Agentic AI to Banking and Insurance Companies

headline: What AI means for finance graduates: fewer entry roles, but faster career paths
summary: As anxiety grows that artificial intelligence will replace human labour, young finance professionals are confronting a harsher reality: entry-level work is disappearing fast. Yet with the right skills, mindset and a recovering market, opportunities remain, according to senior bankers and recruiters in Hong Kong.
